{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Decryption","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Decryption","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>在密码学（<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cryptography\">cryptography <small>(en-US)</small></a>）领域，<strong>解密</strong>是指把加密文本（<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Ciphertext\">ciphertext <small>(en-US)</small></a> ）转换成明文<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Plaintext\">cleartext <small>(en-US)</small></a>。</p>\n<p>解密是一个密码学原语：它通过一种称作<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cipher\">cipher <small>(en-US)</small></a>的编码技术，把加密信息转换成纯文本。正如加密一样，解密在当代密码学领域也是通过特有的算法，结合称作<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Key\">key <small>(en-US)</small></a>的密钥来工作。由于算法通常是公开的，若要保证加密安全，就必须确保密钥高度保密。</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Decryption/decryption.png\" alt=\"The decryption primitive.\" width=\"485\" height=\"81\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>解密是<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Encryption\">encryption <small>(en-US)</small></a>的逆过程，如果密钥高度保密，在没有特定密钥的前提下从数学计算的角度来看，解密是很难做到的。这就取决于算法有多坚固，以及<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cryptanalysis\">cryptanalysis <small>(en-US)</small></a>发展到了什么程度。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技术索引","title":"技术索引","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Encryption_and_Decryption\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Encryption and Decryption</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"在密码学（cryptography (en-US)）领域，解密是指把加密文本（ciphertext (en-US) ）转换成明文cleartext (en-US)。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Decryption","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Descifrado","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Déchiffrement","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Decryption (復号)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Дешифрование","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/decryption","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/decryption/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Decryption","title":"Decryption"}],"pageTitle":"Decryption - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}